text: Wolfenstein is a video game series. Wolfenstein may also refer to: * Wolfenstein 3D, a 1992 game in the series * Return to Castle Wolfenstein, a 2001 game in the series * Wolfenstein (2009 video game), a game in the series * Wolfenstein: The New Order, a 2014 game in the series * Wolfenstein (rock), a rock formation between Tirschenreuth and Hohenwald in Bavaria ==People with the surname== * Eugene Victor Wolfenstein (1940-2010), American social theorist and psychoanalyst * Lincoln Wolfenstein (1923–2015), American physicist ==See also== *Wolfstein (disambiguation)
